The platform uses a commission-based revenue model similar to freelance marketplaces such as Upwork and Fiverr. When a client posts a service request, a percentage of the project budget is retained as a platform fee, while the remaining amount is paid to the professional upon project completion.

	•	React-based frontend
	•	Node.js + Express REST API backend
	•	MongoDB database
	•	JWT authentication with role-based access control
	•	project lifecycle management
	•	platform commission system
	•	admin analytics dashboard

    IT Service Hub is a platform connecting Nigerian tech professionals with international clients for remote IT services.
